Context()->texStrings;
BEGIN_TEXT

Solve the equation \( x - $a = $b \).
$BR
$BR
\( x = \)
\{ ans_rule(10) \}
\{ AnswerFormatHelp("number") \}

END_TEXT
Context()->normalStrings;

################################################
